-- Tokyo Electric Power to Issue New Shares to Fund Expansion, Kyodo Reports
-- B y   F e r g u s   M a g u i r e
-- 2010-09-28T21:11:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/tokyo-electric-power-to-issue-new-shares-to-fund-expansion-kyodo-reports.html
Tokyo Electric Power Co. is
expected to raise several hundred billion yen in a sale of new
shares to fund capital and overseas investments, Kyodo News
reported yesterday, citing unidentified sources familiar with
the matter.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fergus Maguire at 
 fmaguire@bloomberg.net  